#: ../../../reference/tables.md:68
msgid ""
"MyST supports tables like [GitHub Flavoured Markdown][1].\n"
"\n"
"| Header  | Another header |\n"
"|---------|----------------|\n"
"| field 1 | something      |\n"
"| field 2 | something else |\n"
"\n"
"List tables are also a thing:\n"
"\n"
"```{list-table}\n"
":header-rows: 1\n"
"\n"
"* - This is\n"
"  - the header\n"
"  - row\n"
"* - First\n"
"  - row of\n"
"  - very important content\n"
"* - Second\n"
"  - row of\n"
"  - very important content\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"[1]: https://docs.github.com/en/github/writing-on-github/organizing-"
"information-with-tables\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

